{"type":null,"faqId":32694,"title":"蓝牙通话或者听音乐时断续，杂音是什么原因？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>请确认是否各种条件下一直如此，如果是请确认蓝牙存在设备兼容性问题，请您确认对接其它手机是否有类似问题。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果只是某种条件下出现如放在裤兜里，或者放在背包里，放在桌子上，握在手里时，可能是手机天线被遮挡，PLANK的蓝牙天线位于手机上部，当天线被遮挡或者干扰时，通信信号会变差，请您尽量不用手接触到手机上部的天线位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请您尽量不要让手机背面的天线被遮挡，如手机直接贴身放置，贴着金属材质的桌面放置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果您的蓝牙耳机距离手机较远或者隔墙之后，信号强度会减弱，导致信号差。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请确认是否使用了金属材质保护套，金属材质保护套对手机天线有影响，会导致手机信号变差，建议您使用塑料或皮质保护套。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请您检查是否同时在使用手机正在进行WIFI下载。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7396","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748383000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"蓝牙,通话,听歌,听音乐,断续,杂音","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}